@startuml
title 미핏 - 면접 리포트 UI 컴포넌트 구조 (frontend/src/pages/interview-report/)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2196F3
}
skinparam component<<store>> {
  BackgroundColor #F3E5F5
  BorderColor #8E24AA
}
skinparam component<<api>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #FB8C00
}
skinparam component<<print>> {
  BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #607D8B
}
skinparam component<<section>> {
  BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
  BorderColor #0288D1
}

actor "사용자" as U

package "데이터 흐름 (features/interview-session)" {
  component "interviewApi.\ngetInterviewAnalysisReport(uuid)" as API <<api>>
  component "useInterviewSessionStore\n(Zustand)\n+ startReportPolling()" as Store <<store>>
  component "InterviewAnalysisReport\nInterviewQuestionFeedback\nAudio/VideoAnalysisResult\n(TypeScript types)" as Type
}

package "InterviewReportPage (main container)" {
  component "Top Nav\n뒤로가기 + PDF 다운로드" as TopNav
  component "Side Nav\n(scrollspy)" as SideNav
  component "Main Content\n(7 sections)" as Main
}

package "7 Top-level Sections (scrollspy targets)" {
  component "InterviewOverview\n(메타데이터:\ncompany / position /\ndate / duration / difficulty /\nQ 수)" as S1 <<section>>
  component "Summary Section\n(종합 점수 + 코멘트)" as S2 <<section>>
  component "Capabilities Section\n(카테고리 분석)" as S3 <<section>>
  component "StrengthsImprovements\n(강점 / 개선점\n+ evidence)" as S4 <<section>>
  component "AudioAnalysisSection\n(음성 지표 4 카드)" as S5 <<section>>
  component "VideoAnalysisSection\n(표정 분포 + 시선)" as S6 <<section>>
  component "QuestionFeedbackList\n(질문별 탭)" as S7 <<section>>
}

package "Sub-components (visualization)" {
  component "ScoreGauge\n(애니메이션 원형 게이지\n+ 등급 배지)" as SG
  component "RadarChart\n(SVG 레이더 +\n카테고리 progress bars)" as RC
  component "InteractiveTimeline\n(영상 미디어 플레이어 +\n파형 + 발화 segment 표시)" as IT
  component "VoiceAnalysisPanel\n(dBFS 차트 +\n침묵 ratio 시각화)" as VP
  component "TurnMetricCards\n(턴별 4 지표:\nSPM / 필러 / 침묵 / 시선)" as TMC
}

package "Print 전용 (PDF 출력)" {
  component "PrintOnlyContent\n(인쇄 슬롯)" as P1 <<print>>
  component "PrintQuestionFeedbacks\n(인쇄용 질문 피드백)" as P2 <<print>>
}

' === 데이터 흐름 ===
U --> TopNav : 뒤로가기 / PDF 다운로드 클릭
U --> SideNav : 섹션 nav 클릭
U --> Main : 페이지 스크롤

Store --> API : startReportPolling(uuid)\n(status=COMPLETED / FAILED 까지)
API ..> Type : InterviewAnalysisReport 반환
Main --> Store : useStore() 구독\n→ report + isReportPolling

SideNav ..> Main : IntersectionObserver\n(scrollspy 활성 섹션 추적)

' === 컴포넌트 composition ===
Main --> S1
Main --> S2
Main --> S3
Main --> S4
Main --> S5
Main --> S6
Main --> S7

S2 --> SG : overall_score + grade
S3 --> RC : category_scores (4)
S7 --> IT : 답변 영상 + speech_segments
S7 --> VP : audio_analysis_result
S7 --> TMC : turn 별 audio/video 지표

' === Print 모드 ===
Main ..> P1 : CSS @media print
Main ..> P2 : CSS @media print

note right of Main
  Scrollspy 메커니즘:
  IntersectionObserver 가 7 섹션 id 추적
  → 활성 섹션에 SideNav 하이라이트
  click → element.scrollIntoView({behavior: smooth})

  Print: 브라우저 print + CSS media queries
  (ReportLab / PDF 라이브러리 미사용)
end note

footer MeFit - 면접 리포트 UI (FR-REPORT-08, FR-REPORT-10 시각화 컴포넌트)
@enduml
